We wanted the summer house to have a bright, clean coastal feel without over doing it. Elegance with a touch of coastal warmth. The shelves from @jkhomefurnishings add a perfect metallic touch for that desired modern & elegant style. To see more of my home follow my personal page @graceslovefordesigns
